CREATE VIEW [business_rules].[component_s_psa_c_packages]
AS

  SELECT 
    bo.[bk component],         -- Business Key for Hub Component
    bo.[namespace name],       -- [namespace_name] from Satellite Component > PSA > Namespace
    bo.[namespace guid],       -- [namespace_guid] from Satellite Component > PSA > Namespace
    bo.[component name],       -- [package_name] from Satellite Component > PSA > Main
    bo.[almplus status],       -- [component_qlevel] from Satellite Component > PSA > ALMPlus Status
    bo.[layer],                -- [package_layer] from Satellite Component > PSA > AutoSAR
    bo.[component version],    -- [component_version] from Satellite Component > PSA > Main
    bo.[component guid]        -- [component_guid] from Satellite Component > PSA > Main

  FROM [businessobjects].[component_s_psa_c_packages] AS bo
;
